thread.title: Sally P

author: Sally P
title: Sally P
text: I have posted several jobs, received very quick responses and had jobs done within a week. The people doing the jobs have all been friendly, great to deal with and good at what they do. It's a great way to get things done around your house that you don't have the skills, tools or time to do at much more reasonable prices than going to commercial companies. Well worth a try.
